1. Version 1.2

- Correct comments in gen_esme/gen_smsc (Exported callbacks).

- Do not spawn a process for each request. Replace request brokers (processes) 
  by request status (static) information.

- gen_esme_session and gen_smsc_session are almost identical.

  Implement a gen_session to hold code common to gen_esme_session and
  gen_smsc_session

- gen_esme and gen_smsc are almost identical.

  Implement a gen_peer to hold code common to gen_esme and 
  gen_smsc

- Review timers.